<title>HONG KONG: CITIC Beijing mandates FRN issue.</title>
<headline>CITIC Beijing mandates FRN issue.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Beijing headquarters of China International Trust and Investment Corp has mandated CS First Boston to arrange a floating rate note issue, bankers said.</p>
<p>The issue is expected to be about US$150 million in size and have a tenor of three to five years.</p>
<p>--Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2847 4039</p>
